sentences: Gerardo Núñez Díaz (born 29 June 1961) is a Spanish guitarist and composer.
Núñez was born in Jerez de la Frontera (province of Cádiz) in 1961.
In August 2012 his album Travesia reached number 12 on the World Music Charts Europe.
